0.060   2018-09-22 (PERLANCAR)

	- [Bugfix] Fix checking of negative condition.


0.05    2017-07-07 (PERLANCAR)

	- Switch from (ab)using InstallTool phase to using AfterBuild phase
	  to do our stuffs, to be compatible with DZP:StaticInstall.


0.04    2016-12-28 (PERLANCAR)

	- Update check: spec relationship is now expressed using
	  rel=x_spec.


0.03    2016-12-27 (PERLANCAR)

	- Update check: spec relationship is now expressed in
	  DevelopSuggests using _SPEC:: prefix.


0.02    2015-12-17 (PERLANCAR)

	- Allow building of dists like Perinci-Access-Lite or
	  Perinci-Access-Perl which wants to express spec prereq to Rinci
	  but does not actually define Rinci metadata in %SPEC, by checking
	  .tag-implements-Rinci file.


0.01    2015-09-11 (PERLANCAR)

        - First release.
